{"tid":2461242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男警不甘同袍女友一腳踏兩船兼掟煲 　疑施襲致女方多處瘀傷 　審訊後獲判無罪","createTime":"2021-03-25T10:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T10:46:08.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"002d459e74af8e6a76bbba00924ebef0c8810b05","tid":2461242,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xMuiVpiPbsIgbe1n1NXkHpyYYLc=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6QPLSUQOHVHH7BOM6V2EGP6C6A.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxMuiVpiPbsIgbe1n1NXkHpyYYLc%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6QPLSUQOHVHH7BOM6V2EGP6C6A.JPG&h=14e31e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主女警溤嘉茵承認一腳踏兩船<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LVanvod2Rgdr-3cAdkleT95FmwE=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XEOG7RTESFG6JJCGC4XVZOPJ4Y.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLVanvod2Rgdr-3cAdkleT95FmwE%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXEOG7RTESFG6JJCGC4XVZOPJ4Y.JPG&h=7bc9bf20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n甘願當第三者的被告蔡智浩<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n28歲男警明知同屬警員的女友已有男友，仍甘願做第三者，惟女方最終提出分手。男警心有不甘，凌晨到女方寓所理論，其間被指捉緊女方，導致她的手臂及身上有瘀傷，被控普通襲擊罪，案件今日開審。女事主出庭供稱，當日被告欲搶其手機查看，推撞間她失衡跌倒。惟她承認書面口供曾謂「身上嘅瘀傷並不涉及任何襲擊事件」。裁判官杜浩成即日裁決，指當晚女事主同住家人未有目擊或聽到屋內有爭執，女事主亦無向他人表示曾受襲，裁定襲擊不曾發生，被告無罪釋放兼得訟費。<br />\n被告蔡智浩（28歲），控罪書上報稱為公務員。控罪指他於去年8月18日在秀茂坪曉光街富華閣馮嘉茵的住所襲擊馮嘉茵。<br />\n<br />\n冷靜下兩人在房中坐天光<br />\n女事主警員馮嘉茵今作供，透露原有一名林姓綽號「阿鋒」的懲教主任男友。去年5月中，她認識被告，兩人瞞著「阿鋒」拍拖，直至8月馮向被告提出分手，被告在案發當日凌晨到她的寓所理論。<br />\n馮供稱，當晚請被告到她的睡房傾談，其間被告欲查看她的電話，遭她拒絕。及後被告企圖搶電話，更曾捉住她的左前臂約5分鐘，使她感到痛楚。她隨即用右手推開被告並謂：「唔好行埋嚟！」惟她掙扎不果，二人推撞間，她失平衡跌倒，撞到書桌附近的傢俬，但因當時環境昏暗，未有即時查看傷勢。<br />\n當時被告將她扶起，二人冷靜下來，再無爭吵。馮今謂：「之後大家坐喺間房，坐到天光。」早上與被告一同食早餐。<br />\n馮續稱，早上她發現兩邊手臂均有紅腫瘀傷，後來因感冒和咳嗽，在被告陪同下往診所求診，惟無向醫生提及有瘀傷。她解釋道：「以為啲瘀好快散。」<br />\n辯方指，馮當日亦無向朋友提及受襲一事。馮答謂：「我覺得沒有需要同朋友分享。」對於馮母曾問及瘀傷如何弄到，當時馮回答指「公司搬嘢時整親」。馮在庭上解釋因「唔想佢哋擔心，所以冇刻意講」。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210325/SU7ENYO425D5FI5XPHVUCTL3D4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210325%2FSU7ENYO425D5FI5XPHVUCTL3D4%2F&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=7a09727e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210325%2FSU7ENYO425D5FI5XPHVUCTL3D4%2F&h=8b0d201f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210325/SU7ENYO425D5FI5XPHVUCTL3D4/</a>"},{"pid":"1253c4331f23944d32dc415aa7982403d1dff6d5","tid":2461242,"uid":207084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:16:10.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90649f613c8b94ff309affcd77a2edfb0878a07","tid":2461242,"uid":393145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"咁做咩要狗告狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43458d29285fafcfd02f59482966384ac89d61d","tid":2461242,"uid":3086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d90649f613c8b94ff309affcd77a2edfb0878a07","tid":2461242,"uid":393145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"咁做咩要狗告狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:19:49.000Z","msg":"之前新聞提過，係懲教佬叫女曱甴報狗，拉9隻男曱甴"},{"pid":"16f2b2b772d73637ce9b05a6e6bce7750e7936c0","tid":2461242,"uid":254383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:33:09.000Z","msg":"被告蔡智浩（28歲），控罪書上報稱為公務員<br />\n<br />\n連上庭都唔認自己做邊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720e14779cd4830a86544da4ea135b3a2693a50a","tid":2461242,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16f2b2b772d73637ce9b05a6e6bce7750e7936c0","tid":2461242,"uid":254383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:33:09.000Z","msg":"被告蔡智浩（28歲），控罪書上報稱為公務員<br />\n<br />\n連上庭都唔認自己做邊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:34:28.000Z","msg":"係人都知佢係狗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea6a769e8d615649ea87c2c19319626edc60057","tid":2461242,"uid":147856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.dawangmao.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/1563322090-dog-fight-avalon-pier-catalina-island-pit-bulls-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawangmao.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F1563322090-dog-fight-avalon-pier-catalina-island-pit-bulls-3.jpg&h=be761320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示意圖"},{"pid":"1bc00c22ed2a748f3a48b329ce593657ee6d4aad","tid":2461242,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T10:46:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">狗本身就係雜交動物，狗乸俾狗屌就更加係天公地道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"}]}